Throughout their existence, the [[Sith|Sith Order]] established several states, most of which were typically known as the '''Sith Empire''':

==[[Canon]]==
*The '''[[Sith Empire]]''' that existed after the [[Hundred-Year Darkness]]. The [[Sith Lord]] [[Naga Sadow]] was part of the Sith Empire, which participated in the [[Great Hyperspace War]].
*The '''[[Sith Empire (Exar Kun)|Sith Empire]]''' founded by the fallen [[Jedi]] [[Exar Kun]].
*The '''[[Sith Empire (Darth Siberus)|Sith Empire]]''' founded by the [[Sith Lord]] [[Darth Siberus]].
*The '''[[Brotherhood of Darkness]]''', also known as the '''Sith Empire''', was an [[army]] of the Sith before the rise of the [[Galactic Republic]]. Its fall led [[Darth Bane]] to establish the [[Rule of Two]]. {{C|dissolved [[1032 BBY]]}}
*The '''[[Confederacy of Independent Systems]]''' or the '''Separatists'''; though it did not count as a "Sith Empire," it was secretly led by [[Darth Sidious]] and [[Dooku|Darth Tyranus]]. {{C|[[24 BBY]]&mdash;[[19 BBY]]}}
*The '''[[Galactic Empire]]''', which was established by Dark Lord of the Sith [[Darth Sidious]] through the ashes of the [[Galactic Republic]]. It did not count as a "Sith Empire" due to the presence of the Sith being kept a state secret. {{C|Sith rule: [[19 BBY/Legends|19 BBY]]&mdash;[[4 ABY/Legends|4 ABY]]}}
*The '''[[First Order]]'''; though it did not count as a "Sith Empire," it was secretly controlled by Darth Sidious and the [[Sith Eternal]]. {{C|[[21 ABY]]&mdash;[[35 ABY]]}}
*The '''[[Final Order]]''', also known as the '''Sith Eternal fleet''', the '''Sith Empire''', the '''New Order''' or the '''New Empire''', was a Sith fleet of [[Xyston-class Star Destroyer|Star Destroyers]] brought about by the [[Sith Eternal]]. {{C|dissolved [[35 ABY]]}}

==[[Star Wars Legends|Legends]]==
*The '''[[Sith Empire (Pre-Republic)|Sith Empire]]''', named the '''Kingdom of the Sith''', established by the [[Sith (species)/Legends|Sith]] of [[Korriban/Legends|Korriban]] following their victory over the invading [[Rakata/Legends|Rakata]] and relocation to neighbor planet [[Ziost/Legends|Ziost]]. {{C|[[28,000 BBY]]&mdash;[[27,000 BBY/Legends|27,000 BBY]]}}
*The [[Sith Empire/Legends|'''Sith Empire''']], founded by Dark Jedi exiled from the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] after the [[Hundred-Year Darkness/Legends|Hundred-Year Darkness]]. {{C|[[6900 BBY]]&mdash;[[5000 BBY/Legends|5000 BBY]]}}
*The [[Sith Empire (Exar Kun)/Legends|'''Sith Empire''']] under [[Exar Kun/Legends|Exar Kun's]] [[Brotherhood of the Sith]] during the [[Great Sith War/Legends|Great Sith War]]. {{C|[[3997 BBY]]&mdash;[[3996 BBY]]}}
*[[Darth Revan's Sith Empire|'''Darth Revan's Sith Empire''']] during the [[Jedi Civil War]]. {{C|[[3959 BBY]]&mdash;[[3956 BBY]]}}
**The '''[[Sith Triumvirate]]''', a loose alliance of what remained of [[Revan/Legends|Revan's]] Empire {{C|[[3954 BBY]]&mdash;[[3950 BBY]]}}
*The [[Sith Empire (Post–Great Hyperspace War)|'''reconstituted Sith Empire''']] or the '''true Sith''', established by Darth Vitiate ([[Tenebrae]]) from the remains of the "First" Sith Empire. It remained hidden until the [[Great Galactic War]]. {{C|[[4980 BBY]]&mdash;[[3636 BBY]]}}
**The '''[[New Empire]]''' of [[Darth Malgus]] formed from forces of the above empire during the [[Galactic War]]. {{C|[[3640 BBY]]}}
*The [[New Sith|'''New Sith''']] '''Empire''' or the '''reorganized Sith Empire''' founded by the fallen Jedi [[Darth Ruin/Legends|Darth Ruin]] during the [[New Sith Wars]] {{C|[[2000 BBY/Legends|2000 BBY]]&mdash;[[1010 BBY]]}}
**The [[Brotherhood of Darkness/Legends|'''Brotherhood of Darkness''']], founded by [[Skere Kaan]], took the place of the fragmented [[New Sith|Sith Empire]]. {{C|[[1010 BBY]]&mdash;[[1000 BBY/Legends|1000 BBY]]}}
*The [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|'''Confederacy of Independent Systems''']] or the '''Separatists'''; though it didn't count as a "Sith Empire," it was secretly led by [[Palpatine/Legends|Darth Sidious]] and [[Dooku/Legends|Darth Tyranus]]. {{C|[[24 BBY/Legends|24 BBY]]&mdash;[[19 BBY/Legends|19 BBY]]}}
*The '''[[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]''', established by Darth Sidious from the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]], though it didn't count as a "Sith Empire" due to the presence of the Sith being kept a state secret. {{C|Sith rule: [[19 BBY/Legends|19 BBY]]&mdash;[[4 ABY/Legends|4 ABY]]}}
**The [[Dark Empire|'''Dark Empire''']], a faction also ruled by Palpatine which, like a traditional Sith Empire, was ruled with the Emperor's allegiance to the dark side not being hidden. Formed from remnants of the Galactic Empire. {{C|[[4 ABY/Legends|4 ABY]]&mdash;[[11 ABY/Legends|11 ABY]]}}
*The '''[[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances]]''' under the [[New Order (Darth Caedus)|political reign]] of [[Darth Caedus]], though like the Galactic Empire it was not officially considered a Sith Empire. Formed from the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] that took the place of the First Galactic Empire. {{C|Sith rule: [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]]&mdash;[[41 ABY]]}}
*'''[[Darth Krayt's Galactic Empire]]''', also known as the '''Darth Krayt's Sith Empire''', established by [[Darth Krayt]] following the end of the [[Sith–Imperial War]] and the successor state to Darth Sidious' Galactic Empire. Unlike its original incarnation, Sith rule was public and thus it was officially considered a Sith Empire. {{C|[[130 ABY]]&mdash;[[138 ABY]]}}

